data.description: Stop by see this house and make your next home.  The 3-year-old fridge is included.  The refrigerator has a glass door that turns on the inside light for you to see what is inside. 4 Bedrooms with a primary bathroom and an en suite, and an inside utility room.   Open kitchen, breakfast bar, and living room that makes life easier to spend your time together. Covered porch and fenced backyard, waiting to come alive. Meet your neighbors, enjoy the splash pad, kick the ball around, and walk around the lake with a fountain that lights up at night, Fishing Dock, and Magnolia IDS. In the area is great shopping, restaurants, freeways, hospital, and The Woodlands. Double pane windows.  Home is Quality Built. Come find the hidden treasures this area has to offer you. We look forward to seeing you soon.
